atform=pl" data-vars-ga-axid="a40645e2-7533-41e0-91d1-2328e693b2c8" data-trackonomics-xid="fr1756989609544jmk" data-trackonomics-tracking="[utm_source|[utm_campaign|[utm_medium|[gclid|[msclkid|[fbclid|[refdomain|localhost[content_id|f54b0e9e-dcdb-40e7-be79-7c91e31b89d2[content_product_id|9825083f-de75-426f-9890-98ea67b59ec9[product_retailer_id|c7cc9e22-0a40-405f-8cbb-d1b1e8c0a0b1[lt|sale[axid|a40645e2-7533-41e0-91d1-2328e693b2c8]"><s class="css-1leyx4a e1nsrss02">$20</s> $16 at Dermstore</a></div></div></div></div><p data-journey-content="true" data-node-id="25" class="css-i9p093 emevuu60">The cuticle has a very important purpose to serve: It seals the area at the base of the nail. So think twice about cutting or <a href="https://www.goodhousekeeping.com/beauty/nails/" target="_blank" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.goodhousekeeping.com/beauty/nails/" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="removing the cuticle" data-node-id="25.1" class="body-link css-h40fkh emevuu60">removing the cuticle</a>, because it can break that seal of protection, leaving you vulnerable to bacteria and the possibility of infection (as well as painful and unsightly tears). Taking care of your cuticles also helps minimize those dreaded hangnails, Dr. Stern says. </p><p data-journey-content="true" data-node-id="26" class="css-i9p093 emevuu60">If you need to push back your cuticles, Debbie Palmer, D.O., the medical director of Dermatology Associates of New York in Harrison, NY, recommends doing so once per week after you shower (when skin is soft) using a wooden orange stick. Finish by massaging cuticles and nails with a <a href="https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=29069&amp;awinaffid=1264447&amp;campaign=&amp;clickref=|ghk|xid:fr1756989609545ksv&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dermstore.com%2Fproduct_Its%2BA%2BMiracle%2BCuticle%2BOil_62062.htm&amp;platform=pl" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.dermstore.com/product_Its+A+Miracle+Cuticle+Oil_62062.htm" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="cuticle oil" data-vars-ga-product-id="cd0823bd-5763-4d81-be34-a009015208fc" data-node-id="26.1" data-href="https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=29069&amp;awinaffid=1264447&amp;campaign=&amp;clickref=|{subid}&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dermstore.com%2Fproduct_Its%2BA%2BMiracle%2BCuticle%2BOil_62062.htm&amp;platform=pl" data-product-url="https://www.dermstore.com/product_Its+A+Miracle+Cuticle+Oil_62062.htm" data-affiliate="true" data-affiliate-url="https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=29069&amp;awinaffid=1264447&amp;campaign=&amp;clickref=|ghk|xid:fr1756989609545ksv&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dermstore.com%2Fproduct_Its%2BA%2BMiracle%2BCuticle%2BOil_62062.htm&amp;platform=pl" data-affiliate-network="{&quot;afflink_redirect&quot;:&quot;/_p/afflink/bIRK/dermstore-it-s-a-miracle-cuticle-oil&quot;,&quot;site_id&quot;:&quot;8342522f-11a7-4c85-8c15-51f36ee1d53f&quot;,&quot;network&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Trackonomics&quot;},&quot;metadata&quot;:{&quot;trackonomics&quot;:{&quot;network_name&quot;:&quot;awin&quot;}},&quot;product_metadata&quot;:{&quot;8342522f-11a7-4c85-8c15-51f36ee1d53f&quot;:{&quot;network_name&quot;:&quot;awin&quot;,&quot;link&quot;:&quot;https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=29069&amp;awinaffid=1264447&amp;campaign=&amp;clickref=|{subid}&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dermstore.com%2Fproduct_Its%2BA%2BMiracle%2BCuticle%2BOil_62062.htm&amp;platform=pl&quot;}}}" data-vars-ga-product-brand="deborah lippmann" data-vars-ga-product-price="$16.00" data-vars-ga-product-retailer-id="c7cc9e22-0a40-405f-8cbb-d1b1e8c0a0b1" data-vars-ga-product-sem3-brand="deborah lippmann" data-vars-ga-product-sem3-category="Hair Care" data-vars-ga-link-treatment="sale | (not set)" class="body-link product-links css-h40fkh e1aq0z090" data-raw-affiliate-url="https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=29069&amp;awinaffid=1264447&amp;campaign=&amp;clickref=|ghk|xid:{xid}&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dermstore.com%2Fproduct_Its%2BA%2BMiracle%2BCuticle%2BOil_62062.htm&amp;platform=pl" data-vars-ga-axid="ab5dab80-ac95-4b6e-9320-894999948e7c" data-trackonomics-xid="fr1756989609545ksv" data-trackonomics-tracking="[utm_source|[utm_campaign|[utm_medium|[gclid|[msclkid|[fbclid|[refdomain|localhost[content_id|f54b0e9e-dcdb-40e7-be79-7c91e31b89d2[content_product_id|cd0823bd-5763-4d81-be34-a009015208fc[product_retailer_id|c7cc9e22-0a40-405f-8cbb-d1b1e8c0a0b1[lt|sale[axid|ab5dab80-ac95-4b6e-9320-894999948e7c]">cuticle oil</a> or treatment. "Serum-like strengtheners are absorbed quickly and typically contain moisturizers to rehydrate dry, brittle nails," GH Beauty Lab chemist Danusia Wnek says.</p><h2 data-node-id="27" class="body-h2 css-16fdti9 emevuu60"><strong data-redactor-tag="strong" data-node-id="27.0">8. Protect your nails with a base coat.</strong></h2><p data-journey-content="true" data-node-id="28" class="css-i9p093 emevuu60">When you're painting your nails at home, don't <a href="https://www.goodhousekeeping.com/fab-or-fiction/" target="_blank" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.goodhousekeeping.com/fab-or-fiction/" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="skip the base coat" data-node-id="28.1" class="body-link css-h40fkh emevuu60">skip the base coat</a>. Dr. Prystowsky points out that this step both shields the nails from being stained by polish and helps the color look more saturated and opaque with just one coat. Even without color, "strengthening varnishes leave a shiny hard coating on nails; reinforce tips, making them appear thicker; and can protect against damage," says Wnek. And if you really want to take things to the next level, Dr. Shamban suggests adding a coat of clear gloss between each layer to add extra shine and protection. </p><h2 data-node-id="29" class="body-h2 css-16fdti9 emevuu60"><strong data-redactor-tag="strong" data-node-id="29.0">9. Read the labels on your polish.</strong></h2><p data-journey-content="true" data-node-id="30" class="css-i9p093 emevuu60">Just as with makeup and skincare, not all nail polish brands are created equal, so make sure you're buying or using a good product. Dr. Debbie Palmer urges you to steer clear of polishes containing toxic chemicals like dibutyl phthalate, formaldehyde, and toluene, as these toxins can contribute to brittleness, splitting, and cracking.</p><div data-ad-exclude="(min-width: 90rem)" data-embed="embed-product" data-node-id="31" data-theme-key="embedded-product-wrapper" size="small" class="size-small align-right embed css-nygxqo e1ydkxnk0"><div id="product-02cd5f76-066a-45ad-912b-f30fcb59fd84" data-anchor-id="product-02cd5f76-066a-45ad-912b-f30fcb59fd84" class="css-17pp2fn e1ydkxnk1"></div><div size="small" class="size-small align-right css-60ezry ebgq4gw7"><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noskim" data-theme-key="product-image-wrapper" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0016K8B54?linkCode=ogi&amp;tag=goodhousekeeping_auto-append-20&amp;ascsubtag=%5Bartid%7C10055.a.34645%5Bsrc%7Clocalhost%5Bch%7C%5Blt%7C%5Bpid%7C02cd5f76-066a-45ad-912b-f30fcb59fd84%5Baxid%7C59cb4431-ddfb-40bf-8e1e-e4bf33ab4e8d" aria-label="$6 at Amazon for Seche Vite Dry Fast Top Coat" data-href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0016K8B54" data-product-url="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0016K8B54" data-affiliate="true" data-affiliate-url="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0016K8B54?tag=goodhousekeeping_auto-append-20" data-affiliate-network="{&quot;afflink_redirect&quot;:&quot;/_p/afflink/bIRL/amazon-seche-dry-fast-top-coat&quot;,&quot;site_id&quot;:&quot;8342522f-11a7-4c85-8c15-51f36ee1d53f&quot;,&quot;network&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Amazon&quot;},&quot;metadata&quot;:{&quot;links&quot;:{&quot;default&quot;:&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0016K8B54?tag=goodhousekeeping_auto-append-20&quot;,&quot;sem&quot;:&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0016K8B54?tag=ghk-lift-20&quot;,&quot;social&quot;:&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0016K8B54?tag=ghk-soc-lift-20&quot;}